<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body, table, td, p {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .logo-placeholder {
            width: 150px;
            height: 60px;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            display: inline-block;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
<table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
    <tr>
        <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
            <table class="container" role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                    <td align="left">
                        <!-- Logo Placeholder -->
                        <div class="logo-placeholder"></div>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td align="left" style="padding-top: 20px;">
                        <h2 style="font-size: 24px; margin: 0; color: #333333;">Your application to {{.SalonName}}</h2>
                    </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td align="left" style="padding-top: 10px; color: #333333;">
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                            Hi {{.FirstName }},
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                            Thank you for your interest in joining the {{.SalonName}} team and for taking the time to apply.
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                            After careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with other candidates for this role. We truly appreciate your enthusiasm for { {.SalonName}}, and we wish you all the best in your career journey.
                        </p>
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">
                            Warm regards,<br>
                            {{.SalonName}}
                        </p>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>